 your digital marketing is simple but powerful. We focus on the essentials: Website Design, SEO, PPC, SMM, Email Marketing &amp; Re-targeting.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_nr\";s:3:\"100\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_title\";s:18:\"Marketing Strategy\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_text\";s:144:\"We\'re seasoned marketing professionals who take pride in our strategic approach to your business. Its unique and it should be marketed that way.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_nr\";s:3:\"100\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_title\";s:14:\"Graphic Design\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_text\";s:99:\"Brian knows his way around the Adobe Creative Cloud, and has a team of designers when we need help.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_nr\";s:2:\"50\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_title\";s:32:\"Website Management &amp; Geekery\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_text\";s:98:\"Joe speaks fluent geek, managing all things technical and in code for the company and our clients.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_nr\";s:2:\"50\";s:22:\"zerif_ourteam_subtitle\";s:87:\"The number of titles per employee is inversely proportional to the number of employees.\";s:23:\"zerif_testimonials_show\";b:1;s:23:\"zerif_bottomribbon_text\";s:13:\"Already sold?\";s:30:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlabel\";s:12:\"Get in touch\";s:29:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlink\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:22:\"zerif_ribbonright_text\";s:15:\"What about now?\";s:29:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlabel\";s:10:\"Contact us\";s:28:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlink\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:21:\"zerif_contactus_title\";s:10:\"Let\'s Talk\";s:24:\"zerif_contactus_subtitle\";s:133:\"Talk isn\'t only cheap, it\'s free. We\'ll discuss your goals and how we may be able to help before we even ask for payment information.\";s:20:\"zerif_googlemap_show\";b:0;s:23:\"zerif_googlemap_address\";s:16:\"Mount Laurel, NJ\";s:22:\"zerif_googlemap_static\";b:1;s:22:\"zerif_latest_news_show\";b:0;s:10:\"zerif_logo\";s:86:\"http://advertisingbrothers.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/AB-HORZ-Final-Logo_SMALL.png\";s:23:\"zerif_ourfocus_subtitle\";s:33:\"Here are the things that drive us\";s:28:\"zerif_bigtitle_redbutton_url\";s:6:\"#focus\";s:20:\"zerif_ourfocus_title\";s:30:\"<a name=\"focus\"></a> Our Focus\";s:21:\"zerif_socials_twitter\";s:34:\"http://twitter.com/advertisingbros\";s:22:\"zerif_socials_linkedin\";s:40:\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/4857355\";s:24:\"zerif_socials_googleplus\";s:51:\"https://plus.google.com/113818592337118382038/about\";s:16:\"background_image\";s:71:\"http://advertisingbrothers.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/IMG_06273.jpg\";s:17:\"background_repeat\";s:9:\"no-repeat\";s:21:\"background_position_x\";s:6:\"center\";s:21:\"background_attachment\";s:5:\"fixed\";s:25:\"zerif_bigtitle_background\";s:16:\"rgba(0,0,0,0.01)\";s:21:\"zerif_contactus_email\";s:24:\"info@advertisingbros.com\";s:23:\"zerif_contactus_sitekey\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"zerif_email\";s:28:\"info@advertisingbrothers.com\";s:11:\"zerif_phone\";s:12:\"215-253-7146\";s:13:\"zerif_address\";s:16:\"Mount Laurel, NJ\";s:39:\"zerif_bigtitle_1button_background_color\";s:7:\"#dd3333\";s:45:\"zerif_bigtitle_1button_background_color_hover\";s:7:\"#bc0600\";s:39:\"zerif_bigtitle_2button_background_color\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:45:\"zerif_bigtitle_2button_background_color_hover\";s:7:\"#1b07b5\";s:30:\"zerif_buttons_background_color\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:36:\"zerif_buttons_background_color_hover\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:20:\"zerif_footer_socials\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:26:\"zerif_footer_socials_hover\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:31:\"zerif_titles_bottomborder_color\";s:7:\"#e96656\";s:23:\"zerif_ribbon_background\";s:20:\"rgba(221,51,51,0.25)\";s:30:\"zerif_ribbon_button_background\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:36:\"zerif_ribbon_button_background_hover\";s:7:\"#1b07b5\";s:28:\"zerif_ribbonright_background\";s:20:\"rgba(221,51,51,0.25)\";s:35:\"zerif_ribbonright_button_background\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:41:\"zerif_ribbonright_button_background_hover\";s:7:\"#1b07b5\";s:28:\"zerif_ri